long_description: The Richmoor Natural High Organic fruit snacks can be eaten right out of the bag or added to your favorite cereal, yogurt or pancake batter. Choose from mango, apple, banana, strawberry and blueberry. Made from organic fruit that is harvested at its peak. Freeze dry process locks in the flavor and healthy nutrients to give you a tasty snack that can be enjoyed anytime. *Discount will be applied when you check out; offer not valid for sale-price items ending in $._3 or $._9.
